  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd 12 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "12 Indian fishermen arrested in Sri Lankan waters",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The District Magistrate Court has ordered that the 12 Indian fishermen who were arrested for the crime of cross-border fishing in the Sri Lankan waters be remanded till the next 08th.",
        "5 fishermen from Karaikal area of \u200b\u200bTamil Nadu and 7 fishermen from Mayiladuthurai left from Karaikal by boat on 30th.",
        "The said fishermen were caught by the Sri Lankan Navy for the crime of fishing across the border while they were fishing in Parutthurai sea on Sunday 03rd and were taken to the Kangesanturai Naval Camp and detained.",
        "After investigations, the marines produced the fishermen through the Department of Fisheries and Aquatic Resources before the Perth Magistrate's Court today, Monday.",
        "After that the court has ordered to keep them in remand till next 08th."
      ],
